message.body: Both Mom and I have plans for tomorrow that make finding time to talk difficult. How does later today look for you?
Don't know now. I'm at Bagels Best after Torah study. Mom was asleep when I left the house. What works for you?
I don't have any plans. I think Hannah Michelle might be moving in today so I will ask her about her timing.
Ok it is looking like late afternoon or evening is best
Ok. Catch up with you after I speak with Mom.
